title.rendered: TBO Tek Limited joined hands with Smile Foundation to support children’s education

content.rendered:
TBO Tek Limited joined hands with Smile Foundation to support children's education

TBO Tek Limited, joined hands with Smile Foundation to support the education of 150 underprivileged children from marginalized communities which aided in strengthening the existing processes and systems in the Mission Education Centre, Gurugram. In addition to creating and adapting learning opportunities in the current educational landscape, it is ensuring children continue to learn, reduce the incidence of dropouts, increase enrolments, capacitate teaching resources and establish a strong community support network for the sustainability of the centre. The partnership has been able to build an improved, better, and more interesting teaching-learning experience for the students.
